claim: Vincent Cassel starred in a thriller.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Vincent Cassel  (  -LSB- vɛ̃sɑ̃ kasɛl -RSB- ; born Vincent Crochon , 23 November 1966  )  is a French actor best known to English-speaking audiences through his film performances in Ocean 's Twelve and Ocean 's Thirteen , as well as Black Swan .
